        "Lead Generation AI (Capture & qualify leads)",
        "Appointment Booking Bot (Schedule meetings automatically)",
        "Email Automation (Smart email responses & campaigns)",
        "Social Media AI (Content creation & posting)",
        "Document Processing (Invoice, contract automation)",
        "Data Entry Automation (Eliminate manual work)",
        "Sales Assistant AI (Follow-ups & CRM updates)",
        "Internal AI Assistant (Employee productivity tools)",
        "Custom AI Solution (Something specific to your business)"
